# HTTP probe targets — endpoint reachability & latency. Host-specific (edit freely).
# NOTE: the OpenClaw gateway (:18789) is firewalled to the LAN subnet only, so probing it from a
# container fails; its liveness is tracked instead by openclaw_diagnostics_up (loopback textfile scrape).
- targets:
    - https://example.com                       # public digital-twin site
  labels:
    probe: http
